{"tid":1882830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4chan/v/板2019年電腦遊戲獎頒獎禮：Blizzard「光復香港，時代革命」贏得「反遊戲罪行獎」","createTime":"2020-02-16T13:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T02:05:23.000Z","uid":131691,"like":160,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"8abdbfcd5943baffea0bb611ce903a0a2406ed47","tid":1882830,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T13:28:20.000Z","msg":"（背景：/v/係4chan嘅遊戲台，由於4chan傳統，流連/v/嘅，下至全世界最勁嘅弱智，上至全世界最勁嘅癲佬。）<br />\n<br />\n每年年頭，/v/都會對上一年嘅電腦遊戲嚟個大投票，選出嗰年嘅Vidya Gaem Awards，簡稱「/V/GA」。呢個獎標榜「與大衆傳媒嘅電玩獎唔同」，因此會有好多奇怪搞笑嘅獎項，例如：<br />\n「我最憎恨獎」Most Hated Award：全年最乞人憎嘅遊戲<br />\n「差得最少獎」Least Worst Award：差得嚟又差得最少嘅遊戲<br />\n「劇情與角色背景描寫獎」Plot and Backstory Award：最佳描寫女性角色（年年都係H game）<br />\n「噤X就會贏獎」Press X to Win Award：最差遊戲性<br />\n「豬流感獎」Swine Flu Award：2020年回顧2009最佳遊戲<br />\n<br />\nAnyway，今年2020年頭，2019嘅獎終於出爐，香港反送中事件中期爆出嘅「Blizzard暴風雪ban咗香港電競選手Blitzchung（因爲佢喺電競嘅訪問途中講「光復香港，時代革命）」事件被4chan提名競選「反遊戲罪行獎」，以高票擊退其它提名，頒獎禮途中更大大隻字寫出「Liberate Hong Kong, the Revolution of our Time」。<br />\n<br />\n事不宜遲，去片：<br />\n2:13:37 開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XIGcVZg4orA?t=8017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXIGcVZg4orA%3Ft%3D8017&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbuBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=4ee9de37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XIGcVZg4orA?t=8017</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://2019.vidyagaemawards.com/winners#crimes-against-gaming\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F2019.vidyagaemawards.com%2Fwinners%23crimes-against-gaming&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbuBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=4f592efd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://2019.vidyagaemawards.com/winners#crimes-against-gaming</a>"},{"pid":"3780b4718e2fd4edf0694f2776397f2ff551c103","tid":1882830,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T13:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae55a63685b3871d6a8afc02dbebb3b0806e0803","tid":